column5: G'day y'all!
Well here goes .......Like what Lew said....Place looks pretty spiffy.....way to go guys ....
New board looks great!!!!!!!
I've got one of those!  Picked it up at a yard sale for something like $2. Never used it, but I thought it was fun to have.  Mike
Wow this really is the bee's knee's!  Congrats all concerned, and many thanks for all the effort, hardwork and time in making it possible.  Mick
Hey Boys  Loving the new setup!  Cheers  FF

The new board is amazing....I should be working but I have been exploring all of the new options etc., even have "sounds" now...looks great, excellent job!!  bly  PS  The new PM pop up sort of scared me  hehe
LOOKs great....real "purdy" !!!

its a very awsomw board,fishergirl and myself have been surfing around for a while and we love it it will just take a while to figure everything out,a big thanks to the admin and everyone who made this board the way it is.....congrats
Sweet, new board looks awsome. One question. Can we still log into the old board??
Hi all,  New board looks great. Hey, never thought I'd see a "pocket fisherman" again ... I had one at one time. No clue where it is now though.  Pete
Very Nice Indeed!  Cheers, 1leg
WTG on the new site, I can actually post some pics on this one!
Terry are you paying Dano royalties for his avatar?
Man am I slow,you guys got all the low member numbers.....
I have one of them still on the orignal plastic cover bag.........
Your not slow Larry, just that some of us were quicker.
Hi to everyone, I think that I have finally figured this thing out and the board looks real good.  Regards, Sam

Love the new board so far.  Very easy to use and FAST too.
now thats funny

Figgered this was a good thread to try my 1st post on the new board...  ...what the heck, I'll even try posting a pic...  A happy girl with her best bass of the season...    Well maybe not...I thought we could upload pics directly to the board now...I better go read the help section.    Ok... I think this should work.
Wow go to Florida and come back to this !!!  Very nice much nicer on the eyes than the last one.  Thanks
welcome to the new message board lets hope it's a great as the last , what is it now 4 boards have come and gone....and it keeps getting better...cheers Terry
Yes, hello everyone, welcome to the new board.
At least you've got your sig right now Tom!!  Welcome aboard everyone...here we go over another hurdle again!
I'm glad you guys are showing up, I was starting to think I was the only one who saw the link here
Wheres the beer and wings? Joe
Dunno Joe, but I know where the deere sausage is.
Hello everyone. This looks to be a nice facelift to what is already a great site.
Hi guys.  Wow    had a heck of a time getting in, but I think Im OK now.  Gonna set up my signature and avatar now.
everyone seems to be getting things going quickly...the other board was just practice for this one....
Hi guys, I'm in too and must admit, it's lookin pretty spiffy.
Glad to have you in here lew!!  Mondays the day!!
yep looks real good guys. Good work Rick et al!
Hi all.  Just checking to see if all my info got loaded and pic shows.  Joey
To think it all started here
Some of those on ebay the other day Gary! The old pocket fisherman
Where am I???

Post count transfers by PM to a mod Mike.
Wow ... I gotta start all over again as a newbie   Oh welll ... just glad to be here amongst family
thanks Wayne here I thought I would have to reply to every post for the next week with NICE FISH

well hello everyone am i a newbie again?
Man am I ever slow on getting here   I had a senior day yesterday  This is a neato spot to park for awhile.  John

Great work everyone!!! This site is great.  I want to thank everyone involved...the admins, the testers and the entire community.  I'm a relative newbie to OFC...discovered it in September.  I've been members of lots of other boards, but this is by far the best....from the admins to the members....  THANKS!!!
Glad to make it over here....pretty nice lookin'.....just need to figure out all the bells & whistles.      dk
